<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Base-born" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Base-born,</orth> of low birth: <cit><quote>contemptuous b. callet as she is,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.86" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 86</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>better ten thousand b. Cades miscarry,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.8.49" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 49</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to let thy tongue detect thy b. heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.143" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 143</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>